        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "6. Potential Issues or Risks"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Email Uniqueness",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure assumes that the email address uniquely identifies a user. If this is not enforced, it could lead to incorrect results."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Role Changes",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": If roles are frequently updated, ensure that the role data is consistent and up-to-date to avoid incorrect access determinations."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Security",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Ensure that the procedure is protected against SQL injection, although parameterized queries mitigate this risk."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Output Parameters",
